## Project Description

This project is one of the building blocks for a bigger project of my PhD work that looks into the effects of spring timing on the breeding success of alpine birds in central Norway. The study has data from 2019 to 2025 where we have field survey data showing some years of good breeding success and some years of failure.

In order to effectively quantify the timing of spring first, I use camera data from the field sites (the cameras are set up across 7 different plots within the study site). We use

